      "trust.hero.h1": "Built for regulated work.",
      "trust.insight.quote": "โCompliance is not a feature. <span class=\"accent\">It is a property of how the platform is built.</span>โ",
      "trust.hero.lede": "Builtly produces deliverables that an engineer signs under professional liability and that a client uses in court-defensible regulatory submissions. <span class=\"serif\">The platform is built to that standard from the foundation up โ not as a feature bolted on for procurement.</span>",
