      "index.bim.h2": "The platform reads<br/>BIM as design input.",
      "index.bim.lede": "Builtly reads an actual BIM model and turns it into structured engineering input. The platform classifies the elements, proposes the load-bearing system and works out the building's structural principles โ from basement to roof. <em>What was once a model now becomes a basis for decisions.</em>",
      "index.bim.k.project": "Project",
      "index.bim.k.source": "Source",
      "index.bim.k.extents": "Extents",
      "index.bim.k.placed": "Placed",
