      "about.team.s4.focus": "Engineering ยท Investment",
      "hero.side.arch.v": "Rule-driven + hybrid AI",
      "platform.meta.r3.v": "Hybrid AI",
      "about.meta.r3.v": "Hybrid AI",
      "about.glance.c5.v": "Hybrid AI",
      "contact.v.proprietaryAi": "Hybrid AI",
      "index.pipe.s2.l1": "Hybrid AI",
      "about.glance.c5.d": "Multi-engine, deterministic computation. Proprietary models combined with Anthropic and OpenAI capabilities under regulatory boundaries.",
      "platform.f.ai": "Hybrid AI architecture.",
      "plt.found.ai.p": "Hybrid multi-engine architecture combining proprietary engineering models with selectively-invoked Anthropic and OpenAI capabilities. Each request is routed to the engine best suited to the task โ proprietary models for engineering-specific reasoning, third-party models for general language and structured extraction. All engines operate under regulatory boundaries; output is gated by the rule pack, not the AI's confidence.",
      "platform.s01.lede": "The platform is one system with one set of foundations โ hybrid AI orchestrating proprietary, Anthropic and OpenAI models, deterministic computation, regulatory engine, audit trail. Modules are commercial wrappers around the same foundations, priced differently because the market values them differently.",
      "trust.c5.body": "Builtly operates a hybrid AI architecture. Proprietary engineering models are trained on engineering literature, public regulatory text and synthetic engineering datasets โ never on customer project data. Third-party models from Anthropic and OpenAI are invoked through their standard APIs under data-protection terms that prohibit training on customer inputs. Customers who want their de-identified data to contribute to model improvement may opt in under a separate addendum, but the default is no training, no exception, across every model in the stack.",
      "careers.r1.r2.desc": "Build and tune the hybrid AI architecture behind Builtly. Multi-engine orchestration of proprietary, Anthropic and OpenAI models, regulation-constrained inference, and the rule-pack gates that govern output.",
      "careers.pos.1.name": "Senior Platform Engineer",
      "careers.pos.1.desc": "Build the underlying platform that the engineering modules run on. Backend architecture, distributed systems, data pipelines and integration with regulatory data sources. Strong systems engineering background.",
      "careers.pos.1.meta": "Engineering",
      "careers.pos.1.type": "Full-time ยท Remote",
      "careers.pos.2.name": "AI Engineer ยท Hybrid architecture",
      "careers.pos.2.desc": "Build and tune the hybrid AI architecture behind Builtly. Multi-engine orchestration of proprietary, Anthropic and OpenAI models, regulation-constrained inference, vision-based parsing of engineering documents. Senior ML or research engineering background.",
      "careers.pos.2.meta": "AI / ML",
      "careers.pos.2.type": "Full-time ยท Remote",
      "careers.pos.3.name": "Algorithmic Engineer ยท Mathematics",
